text: Sungai Pinang is a neighbourhood in the city of George Town in Penang, Malaysia. Sungai Pinang may also refer to: * Sungai Pinang (Kelantan state constituency), a Malaysian state constituency * Sungai Pinang (Penang state constituency), Malaysia * Bandar Baru Klang (state constituency), formerly known as Sungai Pinang, Selangor, Malaysia
title: Sungai Pinang (disambiguation)
